        {
          "reviewTitle": "It works! Best foundation I've used for YEARS @ age 61!",
          "reviewText": "I've tried it all...but keep using this! I'm almost 61 & have had so many people comment on my \"beautiful skin\"...which if they saw my real face without this foundation, they would not be saying! It makes my face look evened out all day! Of course I powder over it 1-2x's/day, & use blush, but I do have spots from tanning a LOT when I was young (inside & out). Covers all up! Just \"set it\" with a good powder (I recommend Neutrogena Shine Control which I've also used for years & N.'s \"Healthy Skin Blends\" nayiral radiance bronzer which works even on my fair skin! \u0136sorry for double review, but you must have a good, clear palette to work on b4 you use powder & blush & this foundation is IT! (From an artist's daughter.\" When I say years, I'm talking 15+ years!! I'm no young bunny. If it works I stick with it! This works! I'm fair skinned & use a #220. Also, has sunscreen in it - a great bonus!! Great product that's worked since day one... many, MANY years ago!",
