        {
          "reviewTitle": "Reliable Foundation",
          "reviewText": "\u2b50\ufe0f\u2b50\ufe0f\u2b50\ufe0f\u2b50\ufe0f\u2b50\ufe0f Reliable Foundation Revlon ColorStay Foundation (Nude 200): This has been my go-to foundation for years, and it never lets me down. The coverage is medium to full but still feels breathable, and it keeps my skin looking matte all day without getting cakey. I have combination skin, and this foundation really controls shine without drying me out. The shade is just right for me and blends beautifully\u2014plus, I appreciate the SPF protection. I\u2019ve tried a lot of foundations, but I always come back to this one because it\u2019s reliable, affordable, and looks great.",
